{"tid":1508960,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［學術研究］互補色是甚麼？","createTime":"2019-08-26T16:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T17:21:12.000Z","uid":73910,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dac9c44cad628019873175aab6418c42da3a63d5","tid":1508960,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:20:45.000Z","msg":"介紹一下咩叫互補色先：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/win9s4q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwin9s4q.jpg&h=cf67892f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上既色盤入面，兩隻打對面既顏色稱為互補色，<br />\n當互補色重疊時，就會互相抵消，變為較灰暗既顏色。<br />\n舉例，紅色同綠色就係一對互補色，而黃色同紫色又係另一對互補色。<br />\n<br />\n互補色既應用有好多，<br />\n其中一個係職業安全，有d工作需要接觸激光，<br />\n為左保護眼睛，佢地會因應激光顏色而配戴互補色既眼鏡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ryw6vnT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRyw6vnT.jpg&h=802d7675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇新聞，見到一個好有趣既現象，<br />\n有一位人士被多個藍光同綠光照射，但佢好型仔咁禁電話並無視激光，因為佢戴左橙紅色濾鏡既眼鏡。<br />\n<br />\n但跟住無啦啦有人改用紅光，呢位人士就即刻停止玩電話，轉身背對紅光了。<br />\n<br />\n用返互補色個concept：<br />\n橙紅色 vs 藍綠色，所以橙紅鏡可以防到藍綠光。<br />\n但當有人用紅光時，紅光自然可以穿透紅濾鏡。<br />\n<br />\n好簡單既物理，希望呢d小知識可以教得明我d學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：化學老師，好多年無讀物理了，錯concept請指正"},{"pid":"55d44259cf72564d2a55aa4f3114b1c57b35467c","tid":1508960,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:23:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"412ffcd9eee965b4c62aa6ffefbea1268b7b1acc","tid":1508960,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsX4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=37